        <text>
            <body>
                <div type="postcard">
                <pb facs="#farts_1"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline><date>July 8, 1917</date></dateline>
                    <salute>Dear<persName ref="#mother">mother</persName>!</salute>
               </opener>
               <p>Every day I wait a letter from you, but it has been a long time, and no news. 
                  Recently I received the money which you had sent me, thank you. I still live 
                  in the same<placeName ref="#camp">camp</placeName>and I am alive and healthy so far. 
                  Yesterday I had my name day and it had been a long, exhausting 
                  <date notAfter="1917" notBefore="1916">year</date>in the foreign 
                  <placeName ref="#Austria">country</placeName>. I was so sad, woeful and depressed.
                </p>  
                <closer>
                    <signed>Your son<persName ref="#Ivan_Farts">Ivan</persName></signed>
                </closer>
                </div>   
            </body>
